name: [ POST-EFFECT ] LOVERS
description:
Hi, HIC-community!

This is one of GIF-arts from my art-short-film [ POST-EFFECT ] that transmite after party condition and dive into more deep topics about-drugs-contects in our usual life.

No judging, no shaming. Just atmosphere transmission. Post-effect, when you're rethinking expierence after it happen with you and how it influence on your condition when party is over.

The artfilm here: https://youtu.be/Y6RUus-3GoQ

Buying my GIF-arts you are support my film creation, becouse I produce them without any money-support.

It's clean art expression that I want to make my main theme of development in life. For me it's means stop to make job and go into unknown way to dream.

Thank you for support and attention!
